.SH NAME
comet \- a mission editor for Crimson Fields
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.ad l
.hy 0
.HP 6
\fBcomet\fR [\-\-level\ \fIlevel\fR] [\-\-width\ \fIwidth\fR] [\-\-height\ \fIwidth\fR] [\-\-fullscreen\ 1|0] [\-\-sound\ 1|0]
.ad
.hy
.ad l
.hy 0
.HP 6
\fBcomet\fR {\fB\-\-help\fR | \fB\-\-version\fR}
.ad
.hy

.SH "DESCRIPTION"

.PP
\fBcomet\fR (the Crimson Fields Map Editing Tool) is a mission editor for Crimson Fields\&.

.SH "OPTIONS"

.TP
\fB\-\-level\fR \fIlevel\fR
Start the editor with the \fIlevel\fR loaded\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-width\fR \fIw\fR
Set screen width to \fIw\fR\&. Minimum screen width is 320\&. Default is 800\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-height\fR \fIh\fR
Set screen height to \fIh\fR\&. Minimum screen height is 240\&. Default is 600\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-fullscreen\fR 1|0
Turn fullscreen mode on/off\&. The default is to start in windowed mode\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-sound\fR 1|0
Turn sound on/off\&. The default is on\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Print a usage message on standard output and exit\&.

.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Print version information on standard output and exit\&.

